observations.recommendation:
Inventory Committee conducts the physical inventory of all properties and submit the corresponding RPCPPE to the auditor as required under existing regulations, and



The GSO prepares PCs for every class of PPE;



and facilitates reconciliation with the balances in the books of accounts.

Management submits explanation for the delay in the implementation of target priority development projects for the 20% DF.

Expedites and prioritizes the implementation of the remaining CY 2022 projects;

Ensures that target projects for the 20% DF for the succeeding years are fully implemented for timely delivery of socio-economic benefits to its constituents.
